structure.unit: COUNTIES, CITIES, AND OTHER LOCAL UNITS

law.catch_line: No salaries to officers -- No dividends.
law.text: No salary shall be paid to any officer. No dividend shall be declared by the chamber of commerce.
law.history: Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. secs. 2741n-5, 2741n-6.
